    h1=`Welcome back, ${user.username}!`
  else
    h2 Welcome to the Gamestore
  hr
  br
  h2 Inventory
  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p Our store has record counts as follows:

    ul
      li #[strong Games on record:] !{data.game_count}
      li #[strong Games on sale:] !{data.game_instance_count}
